{"tid":1486000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一定要記得 7.1 ：你可以直行，亦可以向右轉！","createTime":"2019-08-18T17:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T20:59:35.000Z","uid":89160,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4ec1ba9e92013f350992119385daa2055aad40e2","tid":1486000,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:39:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家一定要記得 7.1 ，當你行到PP前面，你可以直行，亦可以向右轉！好多手足大叫呼籲，叫大家轉右，但從冇強迫過任何一個人！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>無論你當日係轉右定直行，都係自己人！</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n尊重係雙方面既，唔係多數人就可以大石責死蟹，唔係少數要聽命多數。我地要記得我地當初係點走到今日，唔好令「不割蓆」變成空談！<br />\n<br />\n我地<strong><ins>最起碼</ins></strong>要堅持到《香港人權民主法》通過，大家策略唔同唔緊要，但請你唔好令同你意見唔同前線心灰，隨便指責對方係鬼。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>每一次想叫人 be water 果陣，請你先記起7.1！</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">求求大家。</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"dd1629f6c7a85586bc232bd541177b9adc289602","tid":1486000,"uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:41:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家一定要記得 7.1 ：<br />\n你可以直行，亦可以向右轉！</span></div>"},{"pid":"1ccb8d922042bbf4d27fcf9cd851dcdf038fb247","tid":1486000,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:41:30.000Z","msg":"公民抗命，不分和勇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485672</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bbba2ecfb05fcfb22e81aab47930978c06ff8927","tid":1486000,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:44:53.000Z","msg":"重回 7.1 初心，我先有贏既機會！"},{"pid":"799596a8ca7b1d36f5fc46a7aa33383b8a97a2ba","tid":1486000,"uid":79039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:46:20.000Z","msg":"170 萬人集會之後係Deadline呀！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1484416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1484416</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">推到俾文宣組 民間記者會手足睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非&gt;Deadline&gt;行動升級</span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></div>"},{"pid":"44f1b0ed69943b05d628c37b9037bc1f1c85124d","tid":1486000,"uid":89160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:48:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">7.1 之前，有唔少人話「對冇右轉感到虧欠」，我覺得唔緊要，每個人都有佢能力同睇法，但我地 7.1 當日就係實踐左真正既協作精神。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>我地可唔可以記返起呢一日？</strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"18857aeb3c2d77e8c333926d93ed4756fe7f8a7f","tid":1486000,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ccb8d922042bbf4d27fcf9cd851dcdf038fb247","tid":1486000,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:41:30.000Z","msg":"公民抗命，不分和勇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485672</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:50:51.000Z","msg":"要不分和勇，就係記住兄弟爬山、不割不分<br />\n<br />\n而齊上齊落既意思唔單係「行動一致」，更係「目標一致、矛頭一致」，無論策略有乜唔同，目標都係一致，矛頭指向政權！"},{"pid":"a182061a50a643a4e67ffb599e7bae09958c145b","tid":1486000,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18857aeb3c2d77e8c333926d93ed4756fe7f8a7f","tid":1486000,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ccb8d922042bbf4d27fcf9cd851dcdf038fb247","tid":1486000,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:41:30.000Z","msg":"公民抗命，不分和勇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485672</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:50:51.000Z","msg":"要不分和勇，就係記住兄弟爬山、不割不分<br />\n<br />\n而齊上齊落既意思唔單係「行動一致」，更係「目標一致、矛頭一致」，無論策略有乜唔同，目標都係一致，矛頭指向政權！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20